title: Upgrade your 3D Printer with Printr's Element Eco-System
text:
Expand Printr are showcasing their unique eco-system Dutch startup, Printr's Element USB module plugs into most desktop 3D printers and makes them smarter, easier-to-use and more reliable. We talk to them at TCT Show + Personalize 2015 . 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
